featured.text: The list-based convention, on the other hand, is based on the list of typhoon names compiled in advance by a committee, and is more widely used.

definition.zh_def: 編輯或整理資料以形成一個完整的文件或報告。
definition.en_def: To gather and organize information or data into a complete document or report.
definition.example: The team will compile the research findings into a final report.
